{"word":"Philippi","slug":"philippi","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Philippi</b> A city of Macedonia.<br/> Paul preaches in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=16&verse=40'>Act 16:40</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=20&verse=6'>Act 20:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=52&chapter=2&verse=2'>1Th 2:2</a><br/> Contributes to the maintenance of Paul<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=50&chapter=4&verse=18'>Phi 4:18</a><br/> Paul sends Epaphroditus to<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=50&chapter=2&verse=25'>Phi 2:25</a><br/> Paul writes a letter to the Christians of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=50&chapter=1&verse=1'>Phi 1:1</a>"}]}